thread.title: Explosion in Austin Injures Two People; Unclear if Linked to Package Bombs

author: Dan Frosch
title: Explosion in Austin Injures Two People; Unclear if Linked to Package Bombs
text:
An explosion seriously injured two people in a residential neighborhood in Austin on Sunday night, local authorities said, the fourth blast to occur in the Texas capital since early March.
According to the official Twitter accounts for the Austin Police Department and Austin-Travis County EMS, two males were injured in the explosion and taken to a local hospital with serious but not life-threatening injuries.
